{"tid":614801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉影警嫂裙底　休班警准保釋","createTime":"2018-04-03T00:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T01:20:20.000Z","uid":81228,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cb857d8d3338507dcd829a071a590bb7c89edc0a","tid":614801,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180330/large/30ls3p02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180330%2Flarge%2F30ls3p02.jpg&h=71dd2397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■休班警長莊志強涉偷拍警嫂裙底。<br />\n<br />\n休班警長涉在商場扶手電梯尾隨女子及用手機偷拍她的裙底短片，女子原來是警嫂，發現被跟蹤及偷拍後報警，涉案休班警長在同袍到場前刪除影片。案件昨提訊，他被控作出有違公德行為罪，由於需待辯方索取審訊文件及給他法律意見，他毋須答辯，准保釋候訊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>5月10日再訊</strong><br />\n<br />\n案件昨在觀塘法院提訊，被告莊志強（45歲）報稱是警察，他被指於去年11月27日在油塘大本型商場由地下2樓、2至3樓的扶手電梯作出性質猥褻、淫褻及令人憎惡的行為，即偷拍女事主的裙底。<br />\n<br />\n辯方申請被告毋須答辯，以待向控方索取審訊文件及給被告法律意見，控方不反對辯方申請，亦不反對被告保釋。主任裁判官錢禮將案件押後至5月10日再訊，准被告以現金5,000元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTCC650/18<br />\n■記者戴國輝<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180330/20347416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180330%2F20347416&d=stdLRpnMc9xOK92dHEH%2BLARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=8c430896\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180330%2F20347416&h=c4fe9911\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180330/20347416</a>"},{"pid":"02f81826872337e8ca2b257aa3026d4f32ebb613","tid":614801,"uid":55386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:01:23.000Z","msg":"休班警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986430d62e8445a315e844305f2b46a625a78766","tid":614801,"uid":4285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:01:38.000Z","msg":"淫人妻兒笑呵呵"},{"pid":"48dc49f5ed14c9d920c41bbb1f59cee00744f3f4","tid":614801,"uid":6604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:02:08.000Z","msg":"同袍如兄弟<br />\n老婆一齊砌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16641276287304b01237c4f3b1dce7277d7a1450","tid":614801,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:04:11.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正做乜要蒙面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83dd671e98b4293d82a85e4059db2a3510c9e417","tid":614801,"uid":26675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/03/080629_4a43789112e6a3d3521189e82066fd5a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F03%2F080629_4a43789112e6a3d3521189e82066fd5a.png&h=fc9919f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09a72d4d060642c06fb8508cb2aa9bdda1ffdcf3","tid":614801,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:10:00.000Z","msg":"邊個帶口罩 邊個就係鬼"},{"pid":"4bc6ef66f0ec56f09e4aef88c58be982f2d10c26","tid":614801,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:47:41.000Z","msg":"警方重申..."},{"pid":"50c8486a981e506735740c167e006cadae2eadd6","tid":614801,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:50:40.000Z","msg":"條友係咪delete咗條片"},{"pid":"3172662e70c7c0d3a7c876dda35bd3518b7ba466","tid":614801,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T01:20:20.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}